{
  "stem": "13382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think the end--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--my parents?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mother's parents were dead by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they were not alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was the two-- two married brothers and their families and a single brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are very close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the rest-- all of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole town, they were cleared and that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we never heard anything of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we heard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they-- they said us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They told us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, you know, they-- so you get, I mean, to-- there wasn't even a ghetto, because 20 families.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they said that they'd be going away, and they've been told that they will be OK.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They will work and, you know, just resettling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they took it as a matter resettling, and you know, that God will help, and this will help.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They will come back again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it can't last forever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as they're being taken away, we never heard of them anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We assumed that all of them were taken direct to east Poland or to Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they ended up in a mass grave somewhere, which we have no idea where.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is no sign anymore of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And not only of them, but I think most of the Slovakian Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was a-- a tragedy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, my mother cried bitterly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, it was unbearable, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, you lose one person, is it terrible, but you lose all of them-- you know, it just-- still, for a few months there was some hope.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But after you haven't heard of them, so you took it for granted that they've been-- they've been killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the contact you had with them was by mail?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one-- yes, always.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mail was going continuously.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
